00:27:01.000 --> 00:27:13.000
And so what that means is that Shiny understands how the different components of your app work together, and it makes sure that it only refreshes or changes or refilters or anything like that.

00:27:13.000 --> 00:27:14.000
When it has to.

00:27:14.000 --> 00:27:22.000
